Sentencas: A solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) unit is constructed with Ni-Ce0.9Gd0.1O2 (-) (delta) (GDC) as the anode, yttria-stabilised zirconia (YSZ) as the electrolyte and Pt, Ag or Cu-added La0.58Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 - delta (LSCF)-GDC as the cathode.
Titulo: Oxygen Dissociation and Interfacial Transfer Rate on Performance of SOFCs with Metal-Added (LaSr)(CoFe)O3-(Ce,Gd)O2 - δ Cathodes

Sentencas: The current-voltage measurements are performed at 800 degrees C. Cu addition leads to best SOFC performance.
Titulo: Oxygen Dissociation and Interfacial Transfer Rate on Performance of SOFCs with Metal-Added (LaSr)(CoFe)O3-(Ce,Gd)O2 - δ Cathodes

Sentencas: LSCF-GDC-Cu is better than LSCF-GDC and much better than GDC as the material of the cathode interlayer.
Titulo: Oxygen Dissociation and Interfacial Transfer Rate on Performance of SOFCs with Metal-Added (LaSr)(CoFe)O3-(Ce,Gd)O2 - δ Cathodes

Sentencas: Cu content of 2 wt.-% leads to best SOFC performance.
Titulo: Oxygen Dissociation and Interfacial Transfer Rate on Performance of SOFCs with Metal-Added (LaSr)(CoFe)O3-(Ce,Gd)O2 - δ Cathodes

Sentencas: A cathode functional layer calcined at 800 degrees C is better than that calcined at higher temperature.
Titulo: Oxygen Dissociation and Interfacial Transfer Rate on Performance of SOFCs with Metal-Added (LaSr)(CoFe)O3-(Ce,Gd)O2 - δ Cathodes

Sentencas: Metal addition increases the O-2 dissociation reactivity but results in an interfacial resistance for O transfer.
Titulo: Oxygen Dissociation and Interfacial Transfer Rate on Performance of SOFCs with Metal-Added (LaSr)(CoFe)O3-(Ce,Gd)O2 - δ Cathodes

Sentencas: A balance between the rates of O-2 dissociation and interfacial O transfer is needed for best SOFC performance.
Titulo: Oxygen Dissociation and Interfacial Transfer Rate on Performance of SOFCs with Metal-Added (LaSr)(CoFe)O3-(Ce,Gd)O2 - δ Cathodes
